; Test for issue #781: Setting precision on the command line
; When --round is used, amounts are rounded to their commodity's display
; precision before aggregation, so 10.123 + 20.123 = 10.12 + 20.12 = 30.24
; instead of 30.246 rounded to 30.25.

D 1000.00 EUR

2012-01-01 *
    A                        1 AAA @ 10.00 EUR
    A                        1 BBB @ 20.00 EUR
    C

P 2012-07-01 AAA 10.123 EUR
P 2012-07-01 BBB 20.123 EUR

test bal -V A
           30.25 EUR  A
end test

test bal -V --round A
           30.24 EUR  A
end test
